					<Title
						title="With Background"
						showTitleBackground
						class="break-words"
					/>
					<div class="h-8"></div>

					<Title title="Logo Shown" showTitleBackground logoSrc="/alk-4.png" />
					<div class="h-8"></div>
				</div>
			</article>

			<article>
				<h2>
					<Icon
						name="ri:star-fill"
						width="1.75rem"
						class="inline -mt-2 mr-2"
					/>Page Header
				</h2>
				<p>
					There are several configurations available for the page header. These
					configuration options should make it easy to build a variety of
