					may need to refresh the page to see the animation.
				</p>
				<div class="ml-4 lg:ml-12">
					<PageHeader
						heading="Page Header"
						description="The page header is a component that is used to display the page header."
					/>
					<p>
						Page header with image, background pattern, and pattern highlight.
					</p>
