				</h2>
				<div class="ml-4 lg:ml-12">
					<p class="mb-4">
						Inline code: <Code code=" const x = 42; " lang="js" inline />
						<p class="mt-8 mb-2">Code block:</p>
						<Code lang="astro" code={code} />
